---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Property Maintenance in Eagle Lake & Gouldsboro PA | ABCO"
  description="Year-round property maintenance for homes, businesses, and RV sites near Eagle Lake and Gouldsboro PA — lawn care, seasonal cleanup, deck maintenance, and more."
  canonical="/services/property-maintenance"
>

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Property Maintenance</h1>
      <p>Eagle Lake, Gouldsboro &amp; Covington Township, PA</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="service-detail section">
    <div class="container detail-grid">

      <div class="detail-content">
        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <hr class="orange-line" aria-hidden="true" />
        <p>
          Keeping a property looking its best year-round takes consistent effort. ABCO Landscaping
          provides reliable maintenance programs for residential homeowners, commercial property
          managers, and RV community sites throughout the Eagle Lake and Gouldsboro PA area.
        </p>
        <ul class="detail-list">
          <li>Regular lawn mowing, edging, and blowing</li>
          <li>Fertilization, weed control, and overseeding</li>
          <li>Spring and fall seasonal cleanup</li>
          <li>Leaf removal and debris hauling</li>
          <li>Deck and patio cleaning, repair prep</li>
          <li>General property upkeep and walkthrough</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>RV Community Services</h2>
        <p>
          We have experience working with RV park owners and community associations near Eagle Lake.
          If you manage multiple sites, ask us about our commercial property maintenance packages.
        </p>

        <p>
          For seasonal lawn care tips specific to our area, check out our
          <a href="/blog/year-round-lawn-care-gouldsboro-pa">year-round lawn care guide for Gouldsboro PA homeowners</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="detail-cta">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Request a Free Estimate</a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline">All Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="detail-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-box">
          <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Residential, commercial &amp; RV</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Seasonal programs available</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Free estimates</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Mon–Fri 8 AM – 6 PM</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Sat 9:30 AM – 4:30 PM</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-box sidebar-cta">
          <p>Ready to get started?</p>
          <a href="tel:+17188771197" class="btn btn-primary">📞 (718) 877-1197</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-box">
          <h3>Related Services</h3>
          <ul class="related-list">
            <li><a href="/services/landscaping">Landscaping</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/excavation">Excavation</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #0d0d0d 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2e2e2e;
    padding-block: 3rem 2.5rem;
  }
  .page-header h1 { margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .page-header p { color: #d95210; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; max-width: none; }

  .breadcrumb { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .breadcrumb ol { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.35rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .breadcrumb a { color: #a09890; text-decoration: none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: #d95210; }
  .breadcrumb li[aria-current="page"] { color: #d95210; font-weight: 600; }
  .breadcrumb li[aria-hidden="true"] { color: #404040; }

  .service-detail { background: #0d0d0d; }

  .detail-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }

  .detail-content h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .detail-content p { color: #a09890; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .detail-content a:not(.btn) { color: #d95210; }

  .detail-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .detail-list li { color: #c0b8b0; font-size: 1.1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.5; }
  .detail-list li::before { content: '✓'; color: #d95210; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: 700; }

  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 2rem; }

  .detail-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .sidebar-box { background: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid #2e2e2e; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .sidebar-box h3 { font-size: 1rem; color: #d95210; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .sidebar-box ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .sidebar-box ul li { color: #c0b8b0; font-size: 1rem; }
  .sidebar-cta { text-align: center; }
  .sidebar-cta p { color: #a09890; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; max-width: none; }
  .sidebar-cta .btn { width: 100%; }
  .related-list li a { color: #d95210; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
  .related-list li a:hover { color: #f06520; }

  @media (max-width: 800px) { .detail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
